Saskia Wickham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saskia_Wickham 0 Saskia Wickham (born 14 January 1967) is an English actress best known for playing Alex Wilton in the drama series Boon and Dr. Erica Matthews in the ITV television drama series Peak Practice between 1996 and 1998.
